</div>

<div id="modal03" class="modal bottom-sheet">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <h4>The Vanilla Minecraft Server (Currently Up)</h4>
    <p>
      Our Minecraft server a low-pop survival server with mob griefing is disabled (buildings are safe from creeper explosions!).
      The server runs on Spigot (a fork of Bukkit) which helps with logging and griefer protection.
    </p>
    <p>
      Server rules are simple:<br>
      1. Don't grief.<br>
      2. Don't steal.<br>
      3. Don't be an asshat.
    </p>
    <p>
      How to connect to the Minecraft server:<br>
      &#8226; Fire up Minecraft<br>
      &#8226; From the main menu, click "Multiplayer"<br>
      &#8226; From the "Play Multiplayer" screen, click <u>either</u> "Direct Connect", or "Add server"<br>
      &#8226; Enter <i>server.egee.io</i> as the server address (no IP address required!)<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      And that's it!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

